						 <p>Hey Communism will win! I cackled endlessly while reading this SCP, so I went through the grueling process (not really, this actually was shorter timewise than some SCiPs) and put out an audio version of a SCiP for the first time in over a year. Thanks for the inspiration and I hope you enjoy the homage!</p> <p><a href="https://youtu.be/bKIfinNLtjc">https://youtu.be/bKIfinNLtjc</a></p> <p>Edit: That's fair. Especially egregious since I did it &quot;SCP&quot; the first time and &quot;SCiP&quot; the next two times. Pick a lane!!! (Glad you enjoyed the read though!!)</p> 
				 	]]>
